### Rust ###
# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
debug/
target/

# Cargo.lock is committed: this workspace ships the `host-identity-cli`
# binary. See https://doc.rust-lang.org/cargo/guide/cargo-toml-vs-cargo-lock.html

# These are backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these, which store debugging information
*.pdb

# SBOMs are regenerated on release by the `sbom` CI job and attached to
# the GitHub Release; no need to track working-tree copies.
*.cdx.json

